Im new to FHIR resource development and started using Cruicible for testing. You can find the test results here https://projectcrucible.org/servers/5b7da89704ebd01d0d00001b

Issue:
For US Core Profile test, i see the warnings The server did not return any USCore-Patients. However I see that the server returned the results. What am i missing here. You can see the test @
https://projectcrucible.org/servers/5b7da89704ebd01d0d00001b#5bd8e49c04ebd01c7d000004/uscoretest/US11_Patient

FYI: we have only implemented the Read and Search Operations. hence the test data needed to setup may not have been successful.

Appreciate all the help.
Hi @Srilatha Vemuri -- thanks for your patience. Looks like this is a bug in our test. I created a fix and it is currently being reviewed at: https://github.com/fhir-crucible/plan_executor/pull/145
